      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        {businessType === 'app-marketing'
          ? 'Discover the story behind our app and the team making it happen.'
          : businessType === 'consulting'
          ? 'Learn about our expertise and how we help businesses succeed.'
          : 'Meet the author and discover the inspiration behind the stories.'
